                     <interp inst="t17980110-72-off394" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980110-72-off394" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the 11th of January, two pieces of cotton cloth, called chintz, containing six yards, value 6s.
            </rs> the property of the 
               <persName id="t17980110-72-victim724" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t17980110-72-viclabel395" type="occupation">United Company of Merchants of England, trading to the East-Indies</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-72-victim724 t17980110-72-viclabel395"></join>
